data.description: 3 bed 2 bath mobile home located in the heart of Moss Bluff. Covered drive way and front deck. Large animal enclosure and shelter out back. Roof and skirting was replaced after the 2020 hurricane. Google maps does not have updated street view due to it being a newer property.
